{"tid":2274172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭紀航斥男學生無悔意：如判監不會 14 日咁短","createTime":"2020-11-06T09:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T09:36:57.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"41654b383e948ced7b05c37def0b40c0519bb846","tid":2274172,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"鄭紀航強調，早已裁定被告與母親的說法不可信，但二人仍堅持被告無犯罪，「佢哋點諗係佢哋嘅事，但（辯方指）有悔意，唔同意囉」，「如果監禁（刑期）唔（14 ）天咁短」。案件押後至本月 20 日判刑，官要求先為被告索取額外報告，被告須繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n鄭紀航堅決不索取感化或社會服務令報告，表明「<span class=\"red\">我喺deliberately（故意地）唔會拎感化</span>。如果（專案小組）話唔得，咁就唔拎青少年罪犯評估報告。」<br />\n<br />\n被告楊浩，報稱學生，被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪。控罪指，他於今年11月9日，在金鐘夏愨道及添美道交界近燈柱42387號管有攻擊性武器，即一枝鐳射筆及一枝可伸縮短棍，意圖將其作非法用途。"},{"pid":"f2744785855ca156e33fb1dd9aecf39ff78bc726","tid":2274172,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D%E6%A3%8D%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC-%E5%AE%98%E6%89%B9%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E6%82%94%E6%84%8F-%E5%A6%82%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83-14-%E6%97%A5%E5%92%81%E7%9F%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%25A3%258D%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2582%2594%25E6%2584%258F-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583-14-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2592%2581%25E7%259F%25AD%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9oZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4ac1e8c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%25A3%258D%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B